    <title type="html"><![CDATA[linux下的硬件对应的设备号]]></title>
    <link href="http://thelastday.me/2013/02/15/linux-mount-dev/"/>
    <id>http://thelastday.me/2013/02/15/linux-mount-dev/</id>
    <published>2013-02-14T17:24:21.000Z</published>
    <updated>2013-02-14T17:43:48.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol>
<li><strong>IDE硬盘</strong>  /dev/hd[a-d]（并行硬盘）  </li>
<li><strong>SCSI硬盘</strong>  /dev/sd[a-p]（串行硬盘）  </li>
<li><strong>U盘</strong>   /dev/sd[a-p]  </li>
<li><strong>光驱</strong>  /dev/cdrom  </li>
<li><strong>软驱</strong>  /dev/fd[0-1]  </li>
<li><strong>打印机</strong>    /dev/ld[0-2]  </li>
<li><strong>鼠标</strong>  /dev/mouse  </li>
<li><strong>LCD</strong>   /dev/fb0  </li>
<li><strong>系统终端</strong>  /dev/tty0</li>
</ol>
]]></content>
